ODB - Object Persistency Framework for Ada 95

This directory contains the following directories:

adadoc				- The adadoc component
autoconf			- code for autoconf	
base				- some base components 
bin				- all shell ecripts
doc				- where documentation is stored
etc				- site dependant configuration data
pkg-config

apps				- applications provided by this software
src				- all code for the ODB environment
support				- support code baed on odb and the applications
util                            - utility library 
samples				- some application examples
test				- test code for certain aspects of ODB


After running the configure script, the following directories are generated:

Production results:

	linux-gnu-i686-bin
	linux-gnu-i686-doc
	linux-gnu-i686-include
	linux-gnu-i686-install
	linux-gnu-i686-lib

Others:

var				- where local data is to be stored



